{"id": 1155, "genre": 1000, "title": "这年头你试过哪些假装健康的生活方式？", "description": "不同生活方式的麻烦系数：正常生活<健康生活<假装健康生活。我这个人呢，就是喜欢挑战有难度的。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5332, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160811051720D1GlTUjrzhgEWS6a.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-16T17:00:15Z", "questions": [{"id": 1036, "title": "这年头你试过哪些假装健康的生活方式？", "content": "你都是如何假装健康生活的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 105842, "content": "零食update，吃各种健康口味的饼干巧克力", "image": "img/option/option/20160809113140y72Hd6uPqwa39RIG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105844, "content": "听说坚果营养好，买核桃味的瓜子吃", "image": "img/option/option/20160809120116ZiaRsoQPSV8jzE6U.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105848, "content": "三天吃草，两天烤串", "image": "img/option/option/20160809113819C4A2YV3ZcFtjNJG6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105851, "content": "被伪健康观念洗了脑，只吃水果不吃饭菜", "image": "img/option/option/20160809115748LfHKqbeTM6n8l9FA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105853, "content": "下了一堆健身APP，光对比就用尽毕生力气", "image": "img/option/option/20160809114645fl3FqUxVen1TrJZW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105855, "content": "运动装备买时吃土，买后吃灰", "image": "img/option/option/20160809115023mZ19srTzt7qfIEFL.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105856, "content": "心血来潮就（才）运动，穿拖鞋也要去跑步", "image": "img/option/option/20160809115120c1sFxEThauQXYIPR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105857, "content": "运动打卡，定个闹钟起来打个卡再睡", "image": "img/option/option/20160809115156nJl05pQLBxOuPKqr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105862, "content": "跟所有人说十点前睡觉", "image": "img/option/option/2016080911550439gnkTxKaJIhMmeq.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 105863, "content": "买了净水设备、空气净化器，滤芯一年不换", "image": "img/option/option/20160809120508S8IBdUAnrMKHzvyV.gif